@ciu
title: Convergence and Union (CiU)
face-image: img/parties/logo_ciu.png

**Convergence and Union - <span style='color: #002782; font-weight: bold;'>CiU</span>**
The center-right nationalist federation of the liberal Democratic Convergence of Catalonia (<span style="color: #002782; font-weight: bold;">CDC</span>) and the christian Democratic Union of Catalonia (<span style="color: #0052a3; font-weight: bold;">UDC</span>) has positioned itself as the moderately autonomist with pro-business policies force. It governed Catalonia almost undisputed in the post-Franco autonomy era, and has come back again in 2010 under <span style="color: #002782; font-weight: bold;">Artur Mas</span>, who has long championed fiscal autonomy. Nonetheless, the statute reform's partial rollback fueled internal debates on independence. In 2012, it faces strong austerity backlash and a voter shift to harder-line pro-independence options.

- @ciu_2: Yes, I am a convergent!
- @party_selection: No, select a different party.


@ciu_2
choose-if: 1==0
unavailable-subtitle: Work in progress...
on-arrival: player_party = "ciu"; player_party_name = "<span style='color: #002782; font-weight: bold;'>CiU</span>"; position_disp = "<span style='color: #002782;'>Generalitat (minority government)</span>";
go-to: intros

@cup
title: Popular Unity Candidacy (CUP)
face-image: img/parties/logo_cup.svg

**Popular Unity Candidacy - <span style='color: #C4B156; font-weight: bold;'>CUP</span>**
The far-left, anti-capitalist, eco-socialist platform demands direct democracy, independence, and municipalism. Emerging from 1980s local assemblies, until recently it had a strong grassroots focus and avoided institutions. In 2012, it is getting ready for its first elections, posing as the "left alternative" and pledging one-term mandates and anti-austerity. How much it is able to scale nationally may very well depend on its ability to remain internally coherent and united.

- @cup_2: Yes, it's the time of the peoples!
- @party_selection: No, select a different party.


